290
00:20:52,820 --> 00:20:55,710
Th-They're so strong!

291
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:58,910
Hooray for the Magic Knights!

292
00:20:58,910 --> 00:21:07,740
Hooray! Hooray!

293
00:21:00,780 --> 00:21:03,270
It's too early for you to
be cheering just yet.

