00:21:34,230 --> 00:21:39,600
My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day

298
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:42,570
And push me forward

299
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:44,610
(I can't find a place to go)

300
00:21:44,610 --> 00:21:49,890
Even the faintest light can
still break through the darkness

301
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:55,390
And change the flow of time

302
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:57,810
(I will keep believing in you)

303
00:21:56,810 --> 00:22:00,690
In this ever-vivid place

304
00:22:00,690 --> 00:22:03,630
(Break free yourself)

305
00:22:03,630 --> 00:22:06,530
In order to grasp my endless dream

306
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:09,190
If there is a path that I should choose

307
00:22:09,190 --> 00:22:11,250
(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)

308
00:22:11,250 --> 00:22:14,160
Wherever it may lead us

309
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:16,650
Until my life comes to an end

310
00:22:16,650 --> 00:22:19,330
I will accept any pain that comes my way

311
00:22:19,330 --> 00:22:21,350
